Following severe flooding in Johannesburg on Wednesday night, 9 November, the South African Weather Service has issued a warning of more heavy rains underway for Gauteng on Thursday, 10 November.&nbsp;Gauteng Weather tweeted saying the heavy rains, severe thunderstorms and hail can be expected between 12:00 and 23:00 on Thursday.The SA Weather Service warns that thunderstoms will spread to places over the central and eastern Free State, eastern parts of the North West, Mpumalanga highveld, Gauteng and southern parts of Limpopo on Thursday.&nbsp;The rain in Gauteng is expected to carry through to Friday.&nbsp;